optimized_sql: WITH date_prefilter AS (SELECT d_date_sk FROM date_dim WHERE d_year = 2002), addr_prefilter AS (SELECT ca_address_sk, ca_state FROM customer_address), fact_agg AS (SELECT cr.cr_returning_customer_sk AS ctr_customer_sk, a.ca_state AS ctr_state, SUM(cr.cr_return_amt_inc_tax) AS ctr_total_return FROM catalog_returns cr INNER JOIN date_prefilter d ON cr.cr_returned_date_sk = d.d_date_sk INNER JOIN addr_prefilter a ON cr.cr_returning_addr_sk = a.ca_address_sk GROUP BY cr.cr_returning_customer_sk, a.ca_state), state_avg AS (SELECT ctr_state, AVG(ctr_total_return) * 1.2 AS state_avg_threshold FROM fact_agg GROUP BY ctr_state) SELECT c_customer_id, c_salutation, c_first_name, c_last_name, ca_street_number, ca_street_name, ca_street_type, ca_suite_number, ca_city, ca_county, ca_state, ca_zip, ca_country, ca_gmt_offset, ca_location_type, ctr1.ctr_total_return FROM fact_agg ctr1 INNER JOIN state_avg sa ON ctr1.ctr_state = sa.ctr_state INNER JOIN customer c ON ctr1.ctr_customer_sk = c.c_customer_sk INNER JOIN customer_address ca ON ca.ca_address_sk = c.c_current_addr_sk WHERE ca.ca_state = 'OH' AND ctr1.ctr_total_return > sa.state_avg_threshold ORDER BY c_customer_id, c_salutation, c_first_name, c_last_name, ca_street_number, ca_street_name, ca_street_type, ca_suite_number, ca_city, ca_county, ca_state, ca_zip, ca_country, ca_gmt_offset, ca_location_type, ctr1.ctr_total_return LIMIT 100
